]] |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6OmxaKD7t?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/12/11/grand-theft-auto-v-gets-deathmatch-and-race-creator-update |archivedate=12 April 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"IGN review\">{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/10/22/grand-theft-auto-online-review |accessdate=12 April 2014 |title=Grand Theft Auto Online Review |last1=MacDonald |first1=Keza |date=22 October 2013 |work=[[IGN]] |publisher=[[Ziff Davis]] |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Omxabh3z?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/10/22/grand-theft-auto-online-review |archivedate=12 April 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Shacknews: weeks after\">{{cite web |url=http://www.shacknews.com/article/80678/why-does-grand-theft-auto-online-launch-two-weeks-after |accessdate=12 April 2014 |title=Why does Grand Theft Auto Online launch two weeks after GTA5? |last1=Yoon |first1=Andrew |date=15 August 2013 |work=[[Shacknews]] |publisher=[[GameFly]] |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6OmwPCxgU?url=http://www.shacknews.com/article/80678/why-does-grand-theft-auto-online-launch-two-weeks-after |archivedate=12 April 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<!-- Awards -->\n\n<ref name=\"bafta\">{{cite news |last=Cork |first=Jeff |title=Last Of Us, Tearaway, Grand Theft Auto V Win Big At The BAFTA Awards |url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2014/03/13/last-of-us-tearaway-win-big-at-the-bafta-awards.aspx |work=[[Game Informer]] |date=13 March 2014 |accessdate=27 April 2014}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"GameTrailers\">{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TDu3Nz79BPc |title=Game of the Year Awards 2013 - Best Multiplayer Game |author=GameTrailers |work=[[YouTube]] |publisher=[[Google]] |date=9 January 2014 |accessdate=17 November 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Golden Joystick 19\">{{cite web |url=https://www.pcgamer.com/how-to-watch-the-golden-joystick-awards-2019/ |title=See the Golden Joystick Awards 2019 winners |last=Senior |first=Tom 