 games set in the United States]]\n[[Category:Video games with user-generated gameplay content]]\n[[Category:Windows games]]\n[[Category:Xbox 360 games]]\n[[Category:Xbox One games]]\n", "name_user": "142.160.100.79", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grand_Theft_Auto_Online"}
